$ Registry: HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Notepad

{ Values: fPasteOriginalEOL and fWindowsOnlyEOL

  The values of `fPasteOriginalEOL` and `fWindowsOnlyEOL` specify the handling of
  → development/line-break[EOL characters] when pasting text or pressing enter.

  The default values of `0` will use the currently edited document's detected EOL characters.

  Setting `fWindowsOnlyEOL` to `1` will insert a CR/LF when pressing enter.

  Setting `fPasteOriginalEOL` to `1` will insert the EOL characters as found in the → Windows/clipboard.

}

sa:
  `→ Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/notepad_exe`
